SUNDAY SCHOOL <LOCATION>CELEBRATION</LOCATION> IN PRUSSIA. The Fourth of July was celebrated in <LOCATION>Berlin</LOCATION>, by a German Methodist Sunday school. Two or three hundred children marched from the the Methodist Chapel to the house of our Minister, <PERSON>Mr. Wright</PERSON>, who joined the procession and accompanied it to the public garden, where the scholars amused themselves as our Sunday school do here on similar occasions.
